ulting. He is an avid open source technology enthusiast.\r\n\r\nDamian serves the City of Santa Fe on both the Economic Development Review Committee and the Business and Quality of Life Committee. Additionally, Damian is a co-owner of the experimental arts collective <a href=\"https:\/\/meowwolf.com\/\">Meow Wolf<\/a> which has partnered with George RR Martin to open a 20,000 square foot art experience in Santa Fe.\r\n\r\nDamian graduated cum laude with an interdisciplinary degree in Media Arts and English from the University of New Mexico in 2003. Damian lives in Santa Fe with his wife Lara and two sons, Jack and Henry.","registered":"2011-07-29T22:06:45+00:00","meta":{"links":{"self":"https:\/\/mind.sh\/are\/wp-json\/users\/3","archives":"https:\/\/mind.sh\/are\/wp-json\/users\/3\/posts"}}},"content":"<p>We are currently looking for someone to join our team with solid HTML and CSS skills. The job will entail coding web and app layouts using standard frameworks like Bootstrap and Semantic UI as well as supporting Mindshare clients, troubleshooting, and debugging websites. This is a frontend development position so programming with JS or PHP is a plus, but not required.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mind.sh\/are\/company\/employment\/\">Learn more or apply now \u00bb<\/a><\/p>\n","parent":null,"link":"https:\/\/mind.sh\/are\/news\/now-hiring-frontend-web-designer-htmlcss\/","date":"2015-12-18T20:41:32","modified":"2015-12-22T16:28:24","format":"standard","slug":"now-hiring-frontend-web-designer-htmlcss","guid":"https:\/\/mind.sh\/are\/?p=4330","excerpt":"<p>We are currently looking for someone to join our team with solid HTML and CSS skills. The job will entail coding web and app layouts using standard frameworks like Bootstrap and Semantic UI as well as supporting Mindshare clients, troubleshooting, and debugging websites. This is a frontend development position so programming with JS or PHP&nbsp;<a class=\"mapi excerpt-more\" title=\"Now hiring frontend web designe